data.description: This exceptionally gorgeous timeless traditional is a true show stopper from the moment you drive up! The kitchen & living area will certainly be the setting for many future parties & gatherings with great indoor-outdoor flow leading out to a covered patio & sparkling pool-spa, perfect for hosting the ultimate summer soirée! Gourmet kitchen equipped with a gas burner cooktop, double ovens, gorgeous granite, and hand-scraped hardwoods that flow throughout the main areas! Main level offers a study or 5th bedroom option & primary retreat with ensuite. 2nd floor features a game room with a wet bar-kitchenette area, theatre room with screen & overhead projector with full hookup, a full bathroom, 3 secondary bedrooms----1 with an ensuite bath & all bedrooms have WICs! Highlights: Pre-installed wiring throughout for electronics, built-in blue tooth speakers with individual volume control throughout rooms on 1st floor & patio!
